ella, spinaci, melanzane e peperoni', 8.00, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573821663912-569905455b1c?q=80&w=500'),('Porcina', 'Pomodoro, mozzarella e funghi porcini freschi', 9.50, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604382354936-07c5d9983bd3?q=80&w=500'),('Salame Dolce', 'Pomodoro, mozzarella e salame Milano', 7.00, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1628840042765-356cda07504e?q=80&w=500'),('Cotto e Mais', 'Pomodoro, mozzarella, prosciutto cotto e mais', 7.50, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513104890138-7c749659a591?q=80&w=500');